## ðŸ“¦ Installation

### Option 1: From ZIP File

1. Download the plugin as a `.zip` file from the [GitHub repository](https://github.com/jamshedwolf/learn-qgis).
2. Open **QGIS**.
3. Go to: `Plugins > Manage and Install Plugins > Install from ZIP`.
4. Browse to the downloaded ZIP file and click **Install Plugin**.
5. Activate the plugin if it doesnâ€™t activate automatically.

### Option 2: Manual Install via Git

1. Open your terminal or Git Bash.
2. Clone the repository:
